&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cat /home2/pubdata/ref_data/TBlch_lgst.gff3 | awk -F &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;\t&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;{if ($3==&amp;#34;gene&amp;#34;) print $1 &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\t&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39; $4-5001 &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\t&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39; $5+5000}&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt; LITCHI001829.bed
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id="sambambasamtolols"&gt;sambamba/samtolols&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sambamba slice -L target.bed deduped.bam &amp;gt; sambamba_view_L_target.bam
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;samtools view -hb -L target.bed deduped.bam &amp;gt; samtools_view_L_target.bam
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>提取指定区间含有的基因</title><link>https://Tdxxxx-student.github.io/posts/%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%8C%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%90%AB%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0/</link><pubDate>Wed, 04 Feb 2026 20:41:53 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://Tdxxxx-student.github.io/posts/%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%8C%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%90%AB%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 根据bed文件和gff提取bed区间里头含有什么基因&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;bedtools intersect -a a.bed -b /home2/pubdata/ref_data/Lchinesis_genome.Chr.gff3 -wa -wb &amp;gt; a.bed_intersect_results.txt
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;bedtools intersect -a j.bed -b /home2/pubdata/ref_data/Lchinesis_genome.Chr.gff3 -wa -wb &amp;gt; j.bed_intersect_results.txt
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;bedtools intersect -a w.bed -b /home2/pubdata/ref_data/Lchinesis_genome.Chr.gff3 -wa -wb &amp;gt; w.bed_intersect_results.txt
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/a2cff67c38a9"&gt;bedtools intersect用法 (intersectBed) - 简书 (jianshu.com)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>